title: 2023 DARKHORSE TRAILER Enclosed
offer_description:
Awesome trailer for whatever you can dream up. Obviously it has our decals on it, which can come off easily if needed.       
  We bought it brand new and have used it as a sound and lights trailer, construction trailer, toy hauler, mobile man cave (currently)...if you can dream it, this trailer can probably be used for it.

Ready to hook up and go wherever you need it to go!        
Will get a walkaround video as soon as possible.

title: 2014 CHEVROLET CRUZE LT
offer_description:
Video Test Drive URL (The Nitty Gritty): https://youtu.be/p6nQjJNlaf8        Just the Basics:        
Well.....It's a 1.4 Chevy Cruze and it runs and drives        
It has brand new bolts under the hood on the engine cover, so I'm assuming that someone already did the big job that these typically have and completed the timing and head gaskets. (According the computer, timing degrees are on par with specs).    
    Body has a few dings, but overall it's decent.     
Everything inside works (buttons, heat, windows, etc)        
Suspension seems good. Brakes are fine. Tires are okay.     
    Check engine light shows a couple exhaust codes and auction mentioned a couple others that haven't shown up. Check with me to see if any of this has materialized. Otherwise, I'm fairly impressed with it for what it is.
